{"tid":176554,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"平時做Gym掙扎多些 聞唔聞袋都係操野","createTime":"2017-03-28T09:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T09:12:26.000Z","uid":32102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6aaf274c6818c8008297c350e535ef1e1fac7557","tid":176554,"uid":32102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:02:49.000Z","msg":"經已掙扎怎會看不到<br />\n雖說操你個腹實在有難度<br />\n二頭胸肌無練 如何感覺得到<br />\n不說師兄的袋有多好<br />\n只有一次記得實在接觸到<br />\n懷念師傅給你我 袋底跟我的擁抱<br />\n<br />\n平時做Gym掙扎多些 聞唔聞袋都係操野<br />\n如孩兒能伏於師傅的肩膊 誰也動心<br />\n平時做Gym總有師兄 聞聞袋底不可推卸<br />\n任力威再冷酷 想起佢胸肌 還有袋底 好正"},{"pid":"51e09eb979812759c6b2214747f42e4565b892a1","tid":176554,"uid":36291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔岩音"},{"pid":"fcd09e0f9d2df6dbd0e3756854b0cf65c4a602a1","tid":176554,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca90ef739d555ed3df0cf9b40352f1e9e6aff55","tid":176554,"uid":32102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔岩音</blockquote><br />\n師兄返開教會？"}]}